public class GraphStreamReachabilityGraph extends org.graphstream.graph.implementations.MultiGraph

A GraphStream implementation of ReachabilityGraph.

The graph listens to changes in the reachability graph passed to it via a ReachabilityStateChangedListener. If the reachability graph model is not empty it adds all containing components. The graph implements custom Layouts which can be changed (see also LayoutType).
